' ============================================================

' Supergateways → Ollama
sg1 --> ollama : embed
sg2 --> ollama : embed
sg3 --> ollama : embed
sg4 --> ollama : embed
sg5 --> ollama : embed
sg6 --> ollama : embed
sg7 --> ollama : embed

' Supergateways → mem0_data
sg1 --> mem0vol : read/write
sg2 --> mem0vol
sg3 --> mem0vol
sg4 --> mem0vol
sg5 --> mem0vol
sg6 --> mem0vol
sg7 --> mem0vol

' CLIs → their Supergateway
cli1 --> sg1 : MCP\nstreamableHttp
cli2 --> sg2
cli3 --> sg3
cli4 --> sg4
cli5 --> sg5
cli6 --> sg6
cli7 --> sg7

' CLIs also mount mem0_data (redundant)
cli1 ..> mem0vol : <color:#CC0000>also mounts\n(redundant)</color>
cli2 ..> mem0vol
cli3 ..> mem0vol
cli4 ..> mem0vol
cli5 ..> mem0vol
cli6 ..> mem0vol
cli7 ..> mem0vol

' Ollama → models volume
ollama --> ollamavol : models

